extends ../layout/main
include ../utils/mixins
block variables
    - var pageTitle = 'Главная'

block content

    main
        .container
            include ../includes/breadcrums
            article.article
                h1.article__title Webinar: New Horizons - Europe driving ocean energy development worldwide
                .flex-between.article__details
                    .flex-start.article__points
                        span.event-type.blue Вебинар
                        .flex-start.article__points-wrap
                            time.pin.pin--date 19.02.2020
                            time.pin.pin--time 14:00
                        span.pin
                            svg(width='14', height='20')
                                use(xlink:href='#pin')
                            | Йоханесбург, Южная Африка
                    
                    .share
                        a(href="#", aria-label="Поделиться").link.btn-mode.share__main-btn
                            span.btn
                                svg(width='18', height='15')
                                    use(xlink:href='#share')
                            | Поделиться
                        ul.share__list
                            li.share__item
                                a(aria-label="Закрыть").btn.share__btn--close
                            li.share__item
                                a(href="#", aria-label="Вконтакте").btn.share__btn--vk
                            li.share__item
                                a(href="#", aria-label="Фейсбук").btn.share__btn--fb
                            li.share__item
                                a(href="#", aria-label="Твиттер").btn.share__btn--tw
                            li.share__item
                                a(href="#", aria-label="Одноклассники").btn.share__btn--ok

                .article__wrap.flex-between
                    .article__img-wrap.article__img-wrap--mode
                        img(src="./assets/img/mock/back-1.jpg", width="564", alt="Energy subsidies evolution in the global energy transformation to 2050").article__img
                    .article__info
                        p.article-row
                            span Организаторы:
                            | Eclareon, EuroSolar Russia
                        h3.article-subtitle Краткое описание
                        p Europe has been a pioneer in the development of ocean energy technologies. The vast majority of global capacity is installed in Europe and most projects around the world use European technology. However, other countries are catching up. Canada, the US and China are developing their own markets and new domestic champions are.
                        a(href="#scroll-schedule").link.to-down
                            | Перейти к расписанию
                            svg(width='14', height='14')
                                use(xlink:href='#arrow-down')
                h2.article-subtitle О мероприятии
                .text-block
                    p Europe has been a pioneer in the development of ocean energy technologies. The vast majority of global capacity is installed in Europe and most projects around the world use European technology. However, other countries are catching up. Canada, the US and China are developing their own markets and new domestic champions are starting to emerge. To make the most of its first-mover advantage, both at home and abroad, Europe should act now.
                    p This webinar sought to concretely address this issue by providing useful examples and feedback to policy makers and other stakeholders. IRENA, a global authority on the development of renewable energy, will provide a high-level overview of the state of ocean energy worldwide to set the scene for those unfamiliar with the sector. As the voice of Europe’s ocean energy industry, Ocean Energy Europe will connect EU policy actions with the current successes and future priorities of the sector as it approaches industrialisation.
                table#scroll-schedule.schedule
                    caption.article-subtitle График мероприятий
                    tbody
                        tr.schedule__group
                            th(colspan="2") 1 день
                        +table-row()
                        +table-row()
                        +table-row()
                        tr.schedule__group
                            th(colspan="2") 2 день
                        +table-row()
                        +table-row()
                        +table-row()
                        tr.schedule__group
                            th(colspan="2") 3 день
                        +table-row()
                        +table-row()
                        +table-row()
